<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AI 工具開發控制台</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/xlsx/0.18.5/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/PapaParse/5.4.1/papaparse.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.12.2/firebase-app-compat.js"></script>
<script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.12.2/firebase-auth-compat.js"></script>
<script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.12.2/firebase-firestore-compat.js"></script>
<style>
  :root{
    --ink:#14181F;
    --ink-2:#1D232C;
    --ink-3:#262E39;
    --paper:#F4F1E6;
    --paper-dim:#DAD5C4;
    --line: rgba(244,241,230,0.14);
    --amber:#E8A33D;
    --teal:#4FA37B;
    --coral:#E1614B;
    --slate:#5B7FA6;
    --muted:#8A8F98;
    --font-display: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    --font-body: 'IBM Plex Sans TC', sans-serif;
    --font-mono: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  html,body{margin:0;padding:0;}
  body{
    background:var(--ink);
    color:var(--paper);
    font-family:var(--font-body);
    min-height:100vh;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  ::selection{ background:var(--amber); color:var(--ink); }

  .ticket-header{
    background:var(--ink-2);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    padding:22px 28px 20px;
    position:relative;
  }
  .ticket-header::after{
    content:"";
    position:absolute; left:0; right:0; bottom:-6px; height:6px;
    background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ink) 0 10px, transparent 10px 20px);
    background-size:20px 6px;
    opacity:0.5;
  }
  .brand-row{ display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:14px; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:space-between; }
  .brand-left{ display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:14px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .brand-stamp{
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:11px; letter-spacing:2px;
    color:var(--ink);
    background:var(--amber);
    padding:3px 8px;
    transform:rotate(-2deg);
    display:inline-block;
    border-radius:2px;
  }
  h1{
    font-family:var(--font-display);
    font-weight:600;
    font-size:26px;
    letter-spacing:0.5px;
    margin:0;
    text-transform:uppercase;
  }
  .subline{
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    color:var(--muted);
    font-size:12.5px;
    margin-top:6px;
  }
  .admin-toggle{
    background:transparent;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    color:var(--paper-dim);
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:11.5px;
    letter-spacing:1px;
    padding:8px 14px;
    border-radius:3px;
    cursor:pointer;
  }
  .admin-toggle:hover{ border-color:var(--amber); color:var(--amber); }
  .admin-toggle.on{ background:var(--coral); border-color:var(--coral); color:var(--ink); font-weight:600; }

  .search-wrap{
    margin-top:18px;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    background:var(--ink);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-left:4px solid var(--amber);
    border-radius:3px;
    padding:0 14px;
    max-width:760px;
  }
  .search-wrap span.prompt{
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    color:var(--amber);
    font-size:14px;
    padding-right:8px;
  }
  #q{
    flex:1;
    background:transparent;
    border:none;
    outline:none;
    color:var(--paper);
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:14.5px;
    padding:13px 0;
  }
  #q::placeholder{ color:var(--muted); }
  .go-btn{
    background:var(--amber);
    color:var(--ink);
    border:none;
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-weight:600;
    font-size:12.5px;
    letter-spacing:1px;
    padding:9px 16px;
    border-radius:2px;
    cursor:pointer;
    text-transform:uppercase;
  }
  .go-btn:hover{ background:#f2b25c; }

  .example-row{
    margin-top:10px;
    display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .example-chip{
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:11.5px;
    color:var(--muted);
    border:1px dashed var(--line);
    padding:4px 9px;
    border-radius:20px;
    cursor:pointer;
  }
  .example-chip:hover{ color:var(--paper); border-color:var(--paper-dim); }

  .live-badge{
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px;
    font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:10.5px; color:var(--teal);
    margin-top:10px;
  }
  .live-dot{ width:7px; height:7px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--teal); animation:pulse 1.6s infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse{ 0%,100%{opacity:1;} 50%{opacity:0.25;} }
  .storage-mode-note{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:10px; color:var(--muted); margin-top:4px; }

  .layout{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr 260px;
    gap:0;
    align-items:start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 980px){
    .layout{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .sidebar, .statrail{ order:2; }
    .main{ order:1; }
  }

  .sidebar{
    padding:22px 16px;
    border-right:1px solid var(--line);
    min-height:600px;
  }
  .filter-group{ margin-bottom:24px; }
  .filter-title{
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:10.5px;
    letter-spacing:1.5px;
    color:var(--muted);
    text-transform:uppercase;
    margin-bottom:10px;
    padding-bottom:6px;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
  }
  .multi-tag{ font-size:9px; color:var(--amber); border:1px solid var(--amber); padding:1px 5px; border-radius:8px; letter-spacing:0; }
  .chip-btn{
    display:block;
    width:100%;
    text-align:left;
    background:transparent;
    border:none;
    color:var(--paper);
    font-family:var(--font-body);
    font-size:13px;
    padding:6px 8px;
    border-radius:3px;
    cursor:pointer;
    margin-bottom:2px;
  }
  .chip-btn:hover{ background:var(--ink-2); }
  .chip-btn.active{
    background:var(--amber);
    color:var(--ink);
    font-weight:600;
  }
  .chip-btn.active::before{ content:"✓ "; }
  .chip-btn .count{
    float:right;
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:11px;
    opacity:0.7;
  }
  .reset-link{
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:11px;
    color:var(--coral);
    background:none;
    border:none;
    cursor:pointer;
    padding:0;
    text-decoration:underline;
  }

  .main{ padding:26px 30px; min-height:600px; }
  .section-label{
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:2px;
    color:var(--amber);
    text-transform:uppercase;
    margin:0 0 8px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px;
  }
  .block{ margin-bottom:30px; }
  .summary-text{
    font-size:15.5px;
    line-height:1.75;
    color:var(--paper);
    background:var(--ink-2);
    border-left:3px solid var(--amber);
    padding:16px 18px;
    border-radius:2px;
  }
  .summary-text b{ color:var(--amber); font-weight:600; }
  .summary-text .hint{ display:block; margin-top:8px; font-size:12px; color:var(--muted); font-family:var(--font-mono); }

  .dl-group{ display:flex; gap:8px; }
  .download-btn{
    background:transparent;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    color:var(--paper-dim);
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:10.5px;
    letter-spacing:0.5px;
    padding:5px 10px;
    border-radius:3px;
    cursor:pointer;
  }
  .download-btn:hover{ border-color:var(--teal); color:var(--teal); }
  .download-btn.primary{ border-color:var(--teal); color:var(--teal); }

  table{
    width:100%;
    border-collapse:collapse;
    font-size:13px;
  }
  thead th{
    text-align:left;
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:10px;
    letter-spacing:0.5px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--muted);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    padding:8px 10px;
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  tbody td{
    padding:9px 10px;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    vertical-align:middle;
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  tbody tr.main-row{ cursor:pointer; }
  tbody tr.main-row:hover{ background:var(--ink-2); }
  .proj-name{ font-weight:600; white-space:normal; }
  .proj-name .arrow{ color:var(--muted); margin-right:6px; font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:11px; }
  .num{ font-family:var(--font-mono); text-align:right; }
  .detail-row td{ background:var(--ink-2); white-space:normal; }
  .detail-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px,1fr));
    gap:10px 18px;
    padding:6px 4px 10px;
  }
  .detail-item .k{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:10px; color:var(--muted); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.5px; }
  .detail-item .v{ font-size:13px; margin-top:2px; }
  .hidden{ display:none; }

  .stamp{
    display:inline-block;
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:10.5px;
    font-weight:600;
    letter-spacing:0.5px;
    padding:3px 9px;
    border-radius:20px;
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .stamp-released{ background:rgba(79,163,123,0.18); color:var(--teal); border:1px solid rgba(79,163,123,0.5); }
  .stamp-dev{ background:rgba(91,127,166,0.18); color:var(--slate); border:1px solid rgba(91,127,166,0.5); }
  .stamp-test{ background:rgba(232,163,61,0.18); color:var(--amber); border:1px solid rgba(232,163,61,0.5); }
  .stamp-fix{ background:rgba(225,97,75,0.18); color:var(--coral); border:1px solid rgba(225,97,75,0.5); }

  .insight-list{ margin:0; padding-left:0; list-style:none; }
  .insight-list li{
    position:relative;
    padding:8px 0 8px 22px;
    font-size:14px;
    line-height:1.6;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .insight-list li:last-child{ border-bottom:none; }
  .insight-list li::before{
    content:"—";
    position:absolute; left:0; top:8px;
    color:var(--amber);
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
  }
  .more-note{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:11.5px; color:var(--muted); margin-top:8px; }

  .statrail{
    padding:22px 18px;
    border-left:1px solid var(--line);
    min-height:600px;
  }
  .statrail .filter-title{ margin-bottom:14px; }
  .stat-card{
    background:var(--ink-2);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:4px;
    padding:14px 14px 12px;
    margin-bottom:12px;
  }
  .stat-card .label{
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:10.5px;
    letter-spacing:1px;
    color:var(--muted);
    text-transform:uppercase;
  }
  .stat-card .value{
    font-family:var(--font-display);
    font-size:28px;
    font-weight:600;
    margin-top:4px;
    color:var(--paper);
  }
  .stat-card .value.amber{ color:var(--amber); }
  .stat-card .value.teal{ color:var(--teal); }
  .stat-card .value.slate{ color:var(--slate); }
  .stat-card .value.coral{ color:var(--coral); }
  .scope-note{
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:10.5px;
    color:var(--muted);
    margin-bottom:14px;
    line-height:1.6;
  }

  footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:16px;
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:10.5px;
    color:var(--muted);
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .modal-overlay{
    position:fixed; inset:0; background:rgba(20,24,31,0.78);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    z-index:100; padding:20px;
  }
  .modal-overlay.hidden{ display:none; }
  .modal-box{
    background:var(--ink-2);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-top:4px solid var(--coral);
    border-radius:4px;
    max-width:480px; width:100%;
    padding:24px;
  }
  .modal-box h3{
    font-family:var(--font-display);
    text-transform:uppercase;
    font-size:18px;
    margin:0 0 8px;
    color:var(--coral);
  }
  .modal-box p{ font-size:13.5px; color:var(--paper-dim); line-height:1.6; margin:0 0 16px; }
  .modal-options{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; }
  .modal-opt{
    text-align:left;
    background:var(--ink);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    color:var(--paper);
    font-family:var(--font-body);
    font-size:13.5px;
    padding:10px 12px;
    border-radius:3px;
    cursor:pointer;
  }
  .modal-opt:hover{ border-color:var(--amber); color:var(--amber); }
  .modal-close{
    margin-top:16px;
    background:transparent;
    border:none;
    color:var(--muted);
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:11px;
    text-decoration:underline;
    cursor:pointer;
    padding:0;
  }

  .admin-overlay{
    position:fixed; inset:0; background:rgba(20,24,31,0.92);
    z-index:200; overflow-y:auto; padding:30px;
  }
  .admin-overlay.hidden{ display:none; }
  .admin-box{ max-width:1300px; margin:0 auto; }
  .admin-header{ display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; margin-bottom:18px; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; }
  .admin-header h2{ font-family:var(--font-display); text-transform:uppercase; font-size:22px; margin:0; color:var(--amber); }
  .admin-note{
    font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:11px; color:var(--muted);
    border:1px dashed var(--line); padding:10px 14px; border-radius:3px; margin-bottom:16px; line-height:1.7;
  }
  .admin-actions{ display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center; }
  .btn-primary{
    background:var(--teal); color:var(--ink); border:none; font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-weight:600; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.5px; padding:9px 16px; border-radius:3px; cursor:pointer;
  }
  .btn-secondary{
    background:transparent; color:var(--paper-dim); border:1px solid var(--line); font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:12px; padding:9px 16px; border-radius:3px; cursor:pointer;
  }
  .btn-danger{
    background:transparent; color:var(--coral); border:1px solid var(--coral); font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:11px; padding:5px 9px; border-radius:3px; cursor:pointer;
  }
  .admin-table-wrap{ overflow-x:auto; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:4px; }
  table.admin-table{ min-width:2100px; }
  table.admin-table th, table.admin-table td{ padding:6px 8px; font-size:11.5px; white-space:normal; }
  table.admin-table th{ vertical-align:bottom; line-height:1.3; }
  table.admin-table input, table.admin-table select{
    background:var(--ink); color:var(--paper); border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:2px; font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:11.5px; padding:5px 6px; width:100%;
  }
  table.admin-table input[type=number]{ width:70px; }
  table.admin-table input[type=text]{ width:78px; }
  table.admin-table input[type=date]{ width:128px; }
  table.admin-table input[type=checkbox]{ width:auto; }
  .save-status{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:11.5px; color:var(--teal); }

  /* ---------- Button press feedback ---------- */
  .go-btn, .download-btn, .chip-btn, .admin-toggle, .btn-primary, .btn-secondary, .btn-danger,
  .modal-opt, .example-chip, .reset-link, .modal-close{
    transition: transform 0.08s ease, filter 0.08s ease;
  }
  .go-btn:active, .download-btn:active, .chip-btn:active, .admin-toggle:active,
  .btn-primary:active, .btn-secondary:active, .btn-danger:active,
  .modal-opt:active, .example-chip:active{
    transform: scale(0.95);
    filter: brightness(0.92);
  }

  /* ---------- Toast ---------- */
  .toast-stack{
    position:fixed; right:20px; bottom:20px; z-index:300;
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; align-items:flex-end;
  }
  .toast{
    background:var(--ink-2);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-left:4px solid var(--teal);
    color:var(--paper);
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:12.5px;
    padding:10px 16px;
    border-radius:3px;
    box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    opacity:0;
    transform:translateY(8px);
    animation: toast-in 0.2s ease forwards, toast-out 0.3s ease 2.2s forwards;
  }
  .toast.error{ border-left-color:var(--coral); }
  @keyframes toast-in{ to{ opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }
  @keyframes toast-out{ to{ opacity:0; transform:translateY(-6px); } }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="toast-stack" id="toastStack"></div>

<div class="ticket-header">
  <div class="brand-row">
    <div class="brand-left">
      <span class="brand-stamp">MASTER TRACKER</span>
      <h1>AI 工具開發控制台</h1>
    </div>
    <button class="admin-toggle" id="adminToggleBtn" onclick="openAdminGate()">🔑 管理員入口</button>
  </div>
  <div class="subline">資料基準日 <span id="baseDateLabel">–</span>（今天）・ 共 <span id="totalCountLabel">–</span> 個追蹤專案 ・ 自然語言查詢 + 快速篩選（月份 / 狀態可複選）</div>

  <div class="search-wrap">
    <span class="prompt">Q&gt;</span>
    <input id="q" type="text" placeholder="請輸入問題，例如：目前已經上線的東西 / 6月和7月進度 / 省時最多TOP5" autocomplete="off">
    <button class="go-btn" onclick="runQuery()">查詢</button>
  </div>
  <div class="example-row" id="examples"></div>
  <button class="download-btn primary" style="margin-top:10px;" onclick="openWizard()">🧭 不知道怎麼問？點我一步步找答案</button>
  <div class="live-badge">
    <span class="live-dot"></span>資料即時同步中（每 3 秒自動檢查一次；切回此分頁時也會立即檢查）
    <button class="download-btn" style="margin-left:8px;" onclick="manualRefresh()">🔄 立即刷新</button>
  </div>
  <div class="storage-mode-note" id="storageModeNote"></div>
</div>

<div class="layout">
  <div class="sidebar" id="sidebar"></div>

  <div class="main">
    <div class="block">
      <p class="section-label"><span>① 結論摘要</span></p>
      <div class="summary-text" id="summaryBox">載入中...</div>
    </div>
    <div class="block">
      <p class="section-label">
        <span>② 表格結果</span>
        <span class="dl-group">
          <button class="download-btn primary" onclick="downloadExcel()">⬇ 下載 Excel (.xlsx)</button>
          <button class="download-btn" onclick="downloadCSV()">⬇ 下載 CSV</button>
        </span>
      </p>
      <div style="overflow-x:auto;">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr id="tableHeadRow">
              <th>專案</th><th>組別</th><th>狀態</th><th>開發月份</th><th>上線月份</th>
              <th class="num">省下GD時間</th><th>上線日</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="tableBody"></tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="more-note" id="moreNote"></div>
      <div class="more-note">💡 點任一列可展開查看方向、AI工具開發、AI工具使用者、開發工時、各測試/修復階段等完整欄位</div>
    </div>
    <div class="block">
      <p class="section-label">③ 分析洞察</p>
      <ul class="insight-list" id="insightList"></ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="statrail">
    <p class="filter-title">目前條件統計</p>
    <div class="scope-note" id="scopeNote">全部專案</div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="label">專案數</div><div class="value" id="statTotal">–</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="label">已上線</div><div class="value teal" id="statReleased">–</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="label">開發中</div><div class="value slate" id="statDev">–</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="label">測試/修復中</div><div class="value amber" id="statTesting">–</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="label">平均省下GD時間(hr)</div><div class="value" id="statAvg">–</div></div>
